{"tid":518679,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星 Galaxy A8 / A8+ (2018) 台灣發表，15 日上市","createTime":"2018-01-03T15:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T17:00:42.000Z","uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5dae08229333dba2249f49f76ca4bff3a8260f02","tid":518679,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/230058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F230058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=87b12d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/230131_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F230131_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=246ea965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n三星 Galaxy A8 / A8+ (2018) 台灣發表，15 日上市<br />\n售價分別為 NT$14,990（A8）與 NT$17,990（A8+）。<br />\n <br />\nRoss Wang<br />\n8 小時前<br />\n搭載了許多旗艦機規格如無邊際螢幕、雙鏡頭（前置自拍用的唷）、IP68 防水耐候等規格的三星中階新機 Galaxy A8 (2018) 與 A8+ (2018)，今天正式在台灣登場。在台的版本確認 5.6 吋的 A8 規格為 4GB RAM 與 32GB 儲存空間，建議售價 NT$14,990（約 HK$4,000）；6 吋的 A8+ 則是 6GB RAM 與 64GB 儲存空間，空機 NT$17,990（約 HK$4,800），並有金、黑與紫色可選擇。<br />\n<br />\n規格方面，除了採用 Super AMOLED 面板的 18.5:9 長型 FHD 大螢幕外，還搭載 2.2GHz Dual + 1.6HGz Hexa 的八核心處理器，相機部分 A8 與 A8+ 都搭載 16MP PDAF f/1.7 的主相機，前置雙鏡頭部分則是 16MP + 8MP 的組合，不過光圈都有來到 f/1.9，並支援與 Note 8 類似的景深模擬功能，可提供重新調整景深的功能。還有 Samsung Pay（NFC + MST）、Bluetooth v5.0 與 LTE Cat.11 雙卡雙待（跟記憶卡是獨立的三卡槽）的支援。<br />\n<br />\n2018 年款的 Galaxy A8 系列都預計將會在 1 月 15 日正式開賣，有興趣的朋友可以看看我們的實機圖集參考一下動手玩照片啊！"},{"pid":"26b1f0e2c7d5352357220e9f49c0d2d9a99208f1","tid":518679,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"香港又冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9c20f809729f8f7f89991a76379bc2b7d34871","tid":518679,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26b1f0e2c7d5352357220e9f49c0d2d9a99208f1","tid":518679,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"香港又冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:52:47.000Z","msg":"eprice話淨係得a8+ 月中出"},{"pid":"6529276389ad119ca6bc49fdea926b1f31c61f54","tid":518679,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T17:00:42.000Z","msg":"貴到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}